The following objects where created:

df - this contains the original data set of y2016
misspelled - this shows the value that was mispelled that ends in yyy
y2016 - this data is the same as df, but with the mispelled value removed

y2015 - this is the original y2015 data set

final - this is the merged data set by Name and Gender with counts from both

GirlNames - this is the dataset that only displays Female genders

GirlNames.csv - Csv file containing GirlNames dataframe
